    <section>
      <title>Upgrade Instructions</title>
      <p>Follow these steps to upgrade from v2.x to v3.0.</p>
      <note type="warning">Back up your database before upgrading. This migration is irreversible.</note>
      <ol>
        <li>Stop the application server.</li>
        <li>Run the database migration script.</li>
        <li>Deploy the new application bundle.</li>
      </ol>
    </section>
